N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1225.9 - Permission required to post, distribute or display advertisements, circulars, etc

State Regulations

No person shall post, distribute or display signs, advertisements, circulars, printed or written matter at a truck terminal
without permission. Notes
